    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts reliably through all gears. Both the interior and exterior show minor signs of regular use but are overall clean and well-preserved. It is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner to drive immediately without needing any major repairs.",
