    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "For sale: vehicle in fair condition. The exterior shows visible scratches and several minor dents on the body panels. The interior has noticeable wear, including some stains on the upholstery and thinning carpet. Mechanically, the car is functional and runs, though it shows signs of regular use consistent with its age.",
