    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those who value utility and dependable performance. While the engine and transmission remain solid, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays typical wear, including some fraying on the driver's seat bolster and minor staining on the rear carpets. All essential electronics and safety features are fully functional, though the air conditioning takes a moment to reach peak coldness. It is a well-maintained workhorse that has many miles left, provided the new owner doesn't mind a bit of character in its appearance.",
      "price": 18000.0,
