    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents a premier acquisition for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and presenting in excellent mechanical order, the automobile offers a harmonious balance of performance and aesthetic refinement. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust service history, this unit ensures reliable operation and a commanding presence on the road. We invite you to experience the uncompromising quality and engineering excellence inherent in this exceptional model.",
      "price": 34900.0,
