    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved? This beauty is in great shape and ready for its next adventure. It\u2019s been super dependable for me, and I\u2019ve taken really good care of it. It's perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
