    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery via individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains composed with a factory-spec limited-slip differential and recently refreshed bushings. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, ensuring the high-revving VANOS system operates within optimal parameters. While the aesthetics show minor patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical integrity and throttle response remain sharp. A balanced example for the purist seeking an analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Maintenance up to date. Clear title.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, offering a perfect balance of performance and aesthetic appeal. The exterior finished in its original paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, with only a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful road use. Step inside to a cabin that remains remarkably fresh; the leather seating is soft and free of any punctures or heavy stains, though light creasing on the driver's bolster indicates it has been enjoyed. All interior technology, including the navigation system and heated seats, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs with whisper-quiet precision, backed by a comprehensive service history. We have recently performed a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection to ensure the car is road-trip ready. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. This car represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer looking for a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with the utmost respect.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
